cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.DB, cs.HC, cs.CY. 

The paper discusses documenting spreadsheets using semantic wikis and literate programming, which are both related to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). The use of semantic wikis also involves knowledge representation and management (cs.DB). The objective of creating documentation that is easy to use by those unfamiliar with the spreadsheets suggests a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the title of the paper suggests a potential focus on cyberinfrastructure (cs.CY) as well.
